Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.30,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}In the spring on the riverside I can see the sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.08,0:47:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}And I can feel the heartbreaking smell
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.79,0:47:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}Both of them are running with the wind like they were going to pick up someone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.71,0:47:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}I'm overflowing with tears when I'm with you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.61,0:47:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}I'm starting to yearn for a season that won't return and when we were together
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.30,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord2}haru higure no kawabe ni
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.08,0:47:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord2}setsunai nioi ga shita
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.79,0:47:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord2}kaze wo ukete hashiru futari wo mukae ni kita mitai ni
