Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:48.51,Sign2,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&H38ECED&\fnBrush Script Std\fs40\pos(305.6,506.8)}Itsuka Hi no Ataru Basho de\NSomeday at a Place in the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.02,Sign2,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Dětský domov\NDětská akademie Yotsuba{\i0}
